node.text:
Pick up some rainbow buttercream cakes, pandan chiffon cake and chocolate Swiss roll for tea today. Love these old school bakes and traditional cake shop.

Hope everyone’s enjoying the Hari Raya holidays. Blessed Sunday peeps. 🦄🦄🦄
.
.
.
.
.
THIAM YIAN CONFECTIONERY
Tai Peng Gardens
1004 Serangoon Rd
S534742
I love such old school bakery! But I like to go back Pine Garden flagship store
@makanwarrior Sunset but cloudy day...by the window 👍🏻
@magspie08 I’m dreaming about your curry beef buns Mag 😅
Love this kind of old school chocolate rice Swiss roll 😍😍
Perfection! Sometimes when I make rolls at home, I like to sprinkle them with a little liquor (usually fruit flavored), just a few drops, when it’s on the plate.
I love these as a kid 😍
I love old school cakes 😋💦💦 They are just the best ❤️❤️
